The error is that you are trying to add a String and a Number, which is not
not allowed in Tundra programming language. To fix this, we need to convert
convert the String (which represents number) to Number before addition. So 
the corrected code would be:

```tundra
def normalizeFee(raw) {
  return parseNumber(raw.fee);
}

def normalizePrice(raw) {
  return parseNumber(raw.price);
}

def makeItem(raw) {
  return {
    price: normalizePrice(raw),
    fee: normalizeFee(raw)
   };
}

val raw = {
  price: "32",
  fee: "4"
};

val item = makeItem(raw);
val total = item.price + item.fee;

print(total);
```
